requirement:
During the roll-out phase, when any of the following conditions is met, transition to the landing rollout phase and set the softening time limit to 2 seconds:  
1) The landing gear full compression signal remains true for 12 consecutive frames;  
2) The remote control ground contact signal is true;  
3) The remote control signal status has accumulated 75 frames of abnormal condition. Note that this condition only needs to be checked once.
